title: Biscayne National Park: Places To Go
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Places To Go             Places To Go        Boca Chita Key, the Dante Fascell Visitor Center at Convoy Point and Elliott Key.    Â   With 173,000 acres, there are lots of places to go in Biscayne National Park. Visitors with boats have full access to most of the park, although the shallow nature of the bay and reefs can preclude larger vessels.
